properties.body:
First unveiled on foot at the 2019-2020 Media day, the iconic LeBron 7 arrives in an all-new purple and gold colorway. Rooted in team heritage, the familiar color scheme takes a unique and modern twist with each bold color on the left and right shoe respectively. The premium upper, coupled with innovative Air, ensures that the silhouette pops on both the hardwood and street.

productContent.description:
REP LEBRON IN THE KING'S STYLE.


Unlock your potential in the LeBron 7. The full-length Max Air unit brings you a cushioned jumpstart and shock absorption as you power up for the rebound. It's the seventh signature shoe in the legendary series, scaled down for small 'Brons.


Benefits

  • Max Air cushioning gives impact absorption and responsiveness.
  • An inner sleeve wraps around your foot for a secure feel.
  • Leather and textile upper provides durability for everyday play.

productContent.title: LeBron 7
productContent.subtitle: Men's Shoe
productContent.description:
MADE FOR A KING.


Make your head-turning journey to the top comfortable. Built strong and sleek, the LeBron 7 features a mix of materials on the upper for a look that lasts. The purple and yellow nod to his L.A. endeavors, while metal accents and LeBron crests celebrate the king. Full-length Air cushioning graces your every step.


Clutch Cushioning

Max Air technology is Nike Basketball's largest Air unit to date. It runs the full length of the shoe, delivering responsive cushioning for the court. A foam midsole adds plush comfort during possessions.


Rep LBJ

Bold accents reflect Los Angele's yellow and purple hues. Metal details and LeBron's signature crest honor one of the game's fiercest competitors.


Court-Ready Traction

A rubber outsole offers traction and durability to help you make quick cuts in and out of the paint. It uses bi-colored details that mimic the upper for a unified look.


More Benefits

  • Leather in the upper for a premium look and feel.
  • Padded collar for a soft, comfortable feel.

Product Details

  • Plush foam insole
  • Leather and textile materials in upper
